PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773867709
OL,3,CTaoiseach defends the Prime Minister
OL,4,Cfrom Trump's criticism at the White
OL,5,CHouse
OL,7,FWhen asked by UTV to respond to
OL,8,Fcomments by Irish president Catherine
OL,9,FConnolly ` who criticised "deliberate
OL,10,Fassaults on international law" in the
OL,11,FMiddle East and "the normalisation of
OL,12,Fwar" ` Mr Trump said: "He's lucky I
OL,13,Fexist, that's all I can say."
OL,15,F"Because if you're going to allow
OL,16,Fcountries that are sick and demented `
OL,17,Fand they are demented ` to have
OL,18,Fnuclear weapons, everybody in the
OL,19,Fwhole world should be very thankful."
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@^O]sD@QOUtD@DO]tD@WOUwD@AOU{D@
OL,26,AeO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
