CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773867709
OL,3,CTaoiseach defends the Prime Minister
OL,4,Cfrom Trump's criticism at the White
OL,5,CHouse
OL,7,FHe also said that if the US-Israeli
OL,8,Fattack was not launched on Iran, "you
OL,9,Fwould have had a nuclear war in the
OL,10,FMiddle East and maybe beyond".
OL,12,F"I think it would have hit Europe,
OL,13,Fmaybe not Ireland, but it would have
OL,14,Fhit Europe. It all gets you, it's big
OL,15,Fenough that you would have been
OL,16,Faffected."
OL,26,@pD@bOUrD@]O]tD@AOUxD@JO]
