OL,3,CTaoiseach defends the Prime Minister
OL,4,Cfrom Trump's criticism at the White
OL,5,CHouse
OL,7,FLater on Tuesday, the Taoiseach was
OL,8,Fattending the Friends of Ireland
OL,9,FLuncheon at the US Capitol, ahead of
OL,10,Fhis presentation of a bowl of shamrock
OL,11,Fto the US president back at the White
OL,12,FHouse.
OL,14,FThe deputy First Minister is due to
OL,15,Fhave a scheduled meeting with Mr Trump.
